- Thank you.

539
00:37:04.683 --> 00:37:06.351
4.2 million. Fuck.

540
00:37:07.352 --> 00:37:08.729
- Yeah.
- That's a lot of money.

541
00:37:08.812 --> 00:37:10.397
- Yeah.
- [exclaims]

