570
00:38:52.666 --> 00:38:55.460
"It's never too late
to fix what we broke."

571
00:38:55.544 --> 00:38:57.004
you said the other day.

572
00:38:57.588 --> 00:38:59.923
Just reminding you that.

573
00:39:02.926 --> 00:39:06.180
There was no way we could've known
which way that jury was leaning.

574
00:39:06.972 --> 00:39:12.060
But if I had to do it again…

575
00:39:16.190 --> 00:39:18.150
